**What:** The actual A4 white paper (the `#resume-print-area` div) has no box shadow. It sits flush on the dark container background with only `border border-zinc-800/80` on the parent.

Find the paper container div (line ~435-437, the one with `ref={containerRef}`):

```tsx
// FIND:
className="flex-1 overflow-auto bg-[#0d0d0f] bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_#1a1a2e_0%,_transparent_60%)] flex items-start justify-center p-2 sm:p-4 md:p-8 print-container relative rounded-b-xl border border-zinc-800/80 shadow-inner"

