```

Then find the `{/* Shadow wrapper for depth */}` div (line ~440) and update it:

```tsx
// FIND:
<div 
  className="relative transition-all duration-300"
  style={{
    width: zoom < 1 ? `${794 * zoom}px` : '794px',
    height: zoom < 1 ? `${contentHeight * zoom}px` : 'auto',
  }}
>

// REPLACE WITH:
